          "is_narration"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "qD0_yWgifDM-1",
      "en": "activate the type of sensory neurons called polymodal nociceptors.",
      "ko": "다중모달 통각수용기라는 감각 뉴런을 활성화시키는 것입니다.",
      "tags": {
        "functions": [
          "F04"
        ],
        "situation": "S47",
        "cefr": "B1",
        "register": "R3",
        "emotions": [
          "E09"
        ],
        "expression_types": [
          "X08"
        ],
        "vibe": "V18",
        "power": [],
        "grammar_intent": [],
        "flags": [
          "is_narration"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "qD0_yWgifDM-2",
      "en": "You have these all over your body, including your mouth and nose.",
      "ko": "이것은 입과 코를 포함해 온몸에 있습니다.",
      "tags": {
        "functions": [
          "F04"
        ],
        "situation": "S47",
        "cefr": "B1",
        "register": "R3",
        "emotions": [
          "E09"
        ],
        "expression_types": [
          "X08"
        ],
        "vibe": "V18",
        "power": [],
        "grammar_intent": [],
        "flags": [
          "is_narration"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "qD0_yWgifDM-3",
      "en": "And they're the same receptors that are activated by extreme heat.",
      "ko": "그리고 이것은 극심한 열에 의해 활성화되는 동일한 수용체입니다.",
      "tags": {
        "functions": [
          "F04"
        ],
        "situation": "S47",
        "cefr": "B1",
        "register": "R3",
        "emotions": [
          "E09"
        ],
        "expression_types": [
          "X08"
        ],
        "vibe": "V18",
        "power": [],
